" Tim Pope
Plugin 'tpope/vim-endwise'                " Add 'end' keyword when needed                         | https://github.com/tpope/vim-endwise
Plugin 'tpope/vim-surround'               " Quoting/parenthesizing made simple                    | https://github.com/tpope/vim-surround
